{
  "stem": "14156.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the chickens would have to be [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know how they call that-- killed kosher why-- kosher way, the kosher way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Hitler that time forbid it absolutely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anybody who will do this, they'll-- will be punished or who knows, probably ship them into the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everything was locked up, the doors downstairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My grandma-- you have to have ashes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was ashes on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she took the chicken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes I held it, or my father held it, or my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you, you pluck away the, the feathers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then you cut.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you don't cut it through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You leave the head on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you hold the chicken up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the blood will drop down in the ashes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's is a way how we still killed the chickens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my grandmother wouldn't have done it any other way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother, she came into this, into the, into the house in a way as I understood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father, he, he married the, the, the, the, the father from-- married a woman who was also from his, from his mother-- not mother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my mother had a, a, a brother who was married [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] where, where, his, his-- my father's, my father's sister married the, the brother of my, of my mother.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a double marriage, so to speak of.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when she came, Grandma already was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she reigned the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Grandma reigned the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother had to, somewhere on the line, listen to what Grandma had to say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because she, she was the oldest one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And maybe sometimes, there was some friction in how to cook, and what to cook, what do we have?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
